Package twcore.bots.multibot.bship

Class Summary
bship Battleship Bot This bot regulates the specific attach requirements needed in the battleship arena, manipulates the night mode lvz objects, and hosts battleship main game events.
BSPlayer Represents a player in the main battleship game and stores statistics related to the game in progress.
BSTeam Represents a team of players in the main battleship game.
